                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9975" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1490</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">622 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">拨云见日：极客桥无人机的目标市场选择之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Seeing the Sun: The road to target market selection for Geek Bridge Drones</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董明，耿泽卿，张誉松</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安电子科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江极客桥智能装备股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">目标市场；STP理论；细分市场；利基市场；无人机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Target Market, STP Theory, Market Segmentation, Niche Market, Drones</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例围绕极客桥无人机寻找目标市场、形成市场定位的过程，主要展示了极客桥如何在民用无人机市场中，深度挖掘细分市场的客户需求，找到合适的目标市场，最终打开全新市场的成功实践。极客桥的前身杭一电器在传统遥控器业务逐渐萎缩后，最初选择了航拍无人机市场进行探索，但无人机种类繁多，使用场景多样，同质化的产品很难具有竞争优势。通过进一步分析发现应急照明无人机市场是一个典型的利基市场，极客桥基于这个利基市场的需求完成了针对性的产品设计研发，以系留方案解决了无人机的续航痛点，完美契合了目标市场中的产品需求。通过产品持续改进与品牌建设，极客桥逐渐形成了自身独特的市场定位，并逐步向国际市场进发。本案例旨在以典型的产品创新项目向学生展示企业如何通过对市场环境的分析，识别细分市场，根据自身条件确定目标市场，并且根据目标市场的需求来引导产品创新。学生通过本案例的学习，能够进一步加深对目标市场选择理论和利基市场理论的认识，深刻理解市场营销的核心逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case centers on GeekBridge’s journey in identifying its target market and establishing market positioning for its drones. It primarily demonstrates how GeekBridge, in the civil drone sector, deeply explored customer needs within niche segments to successfully identify a suitable target market and ultimately open up a new market space. Formerly known as Hangyi Electronics, the company initially entered the aerial photography drone market after the decline of its traditional remote control business. However, due to the wide variety of drone types and diverse usage scenarios, its homogeneous products struggled to gain a competitive edge.Further analysis revealed that the emergency lighting drone market represented a typical niche market. Responding to this market’s specific needs, GeekBridge developed a tailored product design. By adopting a tethered solution, the company effectively addressed the pain point of limited drone endurance, aligning perfectly with the demands of the target market. Through continuous product improvement and brand development, GeekBridge gradually established a unique market position and began expanding into international markets.This case is designed as a typical product innovation project to show students how enterprises can analyze the market environment, identify market segments, determine their target market based on internal capabilities, and guide product innovation based on target market needs. Through studying this case, students will deepen their understanding of target market selection theory and niche market theory, and gain a clearer grasp of the core logic of marketing.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">目标市场；STP理论；细分市场；利基市场</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
